{"id":191388,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-20111025/","date":"2011-10-26T00:00:44Z","modified":"2011-10-26T00:00:44Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/10/25","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><span> </span><b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《国家利益》长文：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://nationalinterest.org/article/chinese-nationalism-its-discontents-6038\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的民族主义及其不满情绪</span></a>——</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在军力方面并不算强大，在内政上也不算稳定。它近期对外的强硬表现主要是民族主义在背后撑腰。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">彭博新闻：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/chinese-see-communist-land-sales-hurting-mao-s-poor-to-pay-rich.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国人认为共产党卖地是伤害穷人，喂养富人</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——高地价使得地方政府不惜强拆。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reut.rs/v0aTdb\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国幽灵孕育台湾身份认同</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：记者在高雄访问，民进党支持者反对中国，即使国民党支持者也只是愿意维持现状，以避免和中国武力相向。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://bit.ly/sejSQY\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">计划生育的方方面面</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：有利环境和气候变化？为毛泽东的错误政策买单？富人能生二胎，藏族受到最少限制，一党专制导致世界最严格的人口政策。何时结束？</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://bit.ly/ugkQNW\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国计划生育使用铁腕手段</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：绝育手术很常见，很多省份有报道强制堕胎。而一些曾经大力推广计划生育的官员现在认为这是个错误。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《</span></span><span><span>ABC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">新闻》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://abcn.ws/s2ktzc\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国考虑制定新法定义恐怖活动</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，允许公布恐怖组织名单，以加强应对国内恐怖威胁，支持国际反恐合作。中国曾被指假反恐之名镇压异议分子和少数民族。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/kenrapoza/2011/10/25/why-an-occupy-china-wont-happen/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为什么</span>“<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">占领中国</span>”<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的事情不会象</span>“<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">占领华尔街</span>”<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">那样发生？</span></a>——</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国经济更多考虑的是如何控制人民，而不是控制经济。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-10-25/china-had-best-third-quarter-urban-job-creation-in-years.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国三季度城市新增就业机会创近年来最高值</span></a></span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://onforb.es/sdjcq2\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国是否能够引领共享利益经济？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">介绍共享利益企业概念，以及中国的青年志。</span></span><span><span>Can China Lead The Development Of The Shared Value Economy? </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：中国媒体报道，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reut.rs/sCUgiK\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国广电总局明年将限制记录社会阴暗面的选秀节目</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">；在</span></span><span><span>7:30</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">到</span></span><span><span>10</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">点黄金时间，每家卫视只能播出两部娱乐节目。</span></span><span><span>China orders cutback on TV entertainment </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">读写网：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.readwriteweb.com/archives/us_trails_china_in_almost_every_mobile_usage_trend.php?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+readwriteweb+(ReadWriteWeb)\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在手机应用的各个方面，美国几乎都被中国甩在了身后</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">布鲁金斯学会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.brookings.edu/articles/2011/1021_china_li.aspx?rssid=china&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+BrookingsRSS%2Ftopics%2Fchina+%28Brookings%3A+Topics+-+China%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的悖论和美国的误读</span></a>——</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国进入</span></span><span><span>21</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">世纪的道路充满希望和恐惧。研究中国需要与复杂、含混与不确定打交道。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20111025/ap_on_re_as/as_china_syria\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国派出特使前往叙利亚，称希望叙利亚各方能和平解决危机</span></a></span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20111025/pl_nm/us_usa_china_currency_obama\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">财政部表示，奥巴马将在</span>11<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月中美峰会上就人民币问题向胡锦涛施压</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：美国防长帕内塔称，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://nyti.ms/uaMxL5\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国将在太平洋长期存在</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，并将加强太平洋的军事部署。</span></span><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：美国防部长警告说，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/10/25/panetta-warns-of-china-secrecy/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国军事现代化缺乏透明度，令人感到不安</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：泰国是全球硬盘生产中心，由于今年工厂受到洪水冲击，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://gu.com/p/32pjb/tw\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">可能会影响</span>2012<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年初的全球硬盘供应</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：利比亚过渡委说，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://bit.ly/tXoGpm\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡扎菲及其子穆塔西姆周二早晨在一处秘密地点下葬</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span>Official: Gadhafi buried along with son </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">土耳其地震发生两天后，一位</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://bit.ly/t2H8ke\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">三个月大的早产儿在废墟中获救</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span>Small baby rescued from Turkish quake rubble </span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：在香港召开的彭博中国联线会议上，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://buswk.co/uJtc6Z\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">澳盛银行集团和瑞银发言认为中国经济正在软着陆</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span>China</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">’</span></span><span><span>s Economy Heading for a </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">‘</span></span><span><span>Soft Landing,</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">’</span></span><span><span> ANZ, UBS Say </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：安永发布报告预测，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://on.wsj.com/sC7Yrm\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">如果印度能够很好地控制通胀，其</span>2013<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年的</span>GDP<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">增速将超过中国</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span>RBI Raises Rates, But Some Still See India Beating China </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">彭博新闻：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/buffett-s-chinese-car-investment-fails-to-bring-los-angeles-promised-jobs.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">洛杉矶曾对比亚迪在那里开设美国总部寄予厚望</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，但</span></span><span><span>BYD</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">不但推迟了一年才开设，而且也没能解决什么就业问题。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/why-harley-cant-rev-up-in-china-10202011.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为什么哈雷摩托在中国</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卖不动</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？</span></span><span><span>——</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">地方道路法规限制了哈雷的销售。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约客》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/evanosnos/2011/10/baby-formula-in-macau.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国来信：中国边境最热门的商品</span></a>——</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">这些日子，如果你跨国边境从大陆进入澳门，立刻就会被婴儿奶粉所包围。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/10/25/storming-the-hospital-violence-as-a-first-choice/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">冲击医院：当暴力成为首选手段</span></a>——</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">由于法院一般会偏护医院，采取暴力似乎成为家属获得赔偿的唯一可行手段</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：周末，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://on.wsj.com/sb4PqH\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">不满的业主洗劫了一家降价的售楼处</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。这说明中国打压楼价的政策已经凑效，但也暗示如果措施过度会带来何种后果。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；到iTunes 中搜索“译者”即可订阅和下载译者播客Podcast；点击<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/p/download.html\">这里</a>可以播放和下载所有译者已公开的视频、音频和杂志。（下载需翻墙）。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-3084715940265081455?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"t